3. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking): The paper discusses the state of the art and open research challenges in high-throughput satellites, which falls under the domain of communications and networking. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the challenges in designing and controlling high-throughput satellite systems, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper may involve distributed computing approaches for efficient interference mitigation in high-throughput satellites.
